## HTML → Flutter Widget Mapping (Stitch Workflow)

> **Nguồn:** `vnpt-workflow-stitch2flutter.mdc` — mapping khi generate từ Stitch HTML export.

### HTML Elements → Flutter Widgets

| HTML/Tailwind class | Flutter widget |
|---------------------|----------------|
| `<main class="flex flex-col ...">` | `Column(...)` |
| `<div class="bg-login-gradient">` | `Container(gradient: LinearGradient(...))` |
| `<div class="card-shadow bg-white rounded-xl">` | `Container(boxShadow: [...], borderRadius: ...)` |
| `<h1 class="text-headline-lg">` | `Text('...', style: TextStyle(fontSize: 30, fontWeight: w700))` |
| `<form class="flex flex-col gap-stack-md">` | `Column(crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.stretch, children: [...])` |
| `<input class="rounded-lg border">` | `TextField(decoration: InputDecoration(border: ...))` |
| `<button class="btn-gradient rounded-lg">` | `ElevatedButton(...)` |
| `<span class="material-symbols-outlined">login</span>` | `Icon(Icons.login, size: 20)` |
| `<div class="bg-[#D1E7DD] text-[#0f5132] rounded-lg">` | `Container(color: Color(0xFFD1E7DD), borderRadius: ...)` |

### Material Symbols → Flutter Icons

| Stitch (Material Symbols) | Flutter Material Icons |
|--------------------------|----------------------|
| `mail` | `Icons.mail_outline` |
| `lock` | `Icons.lock_outline` |
| `login` | `Icons.login` |
| `check_circle` | `Icons.check_circle` |
| `arrow_back` | `Icons.arrow_back` |
| `search` | `Icons.search` |
| `close` | `Icons.close` |
| `add` | `Icons.add` |

### Stitch Container Patterns

```dart
// Gradient
Container(
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    gradient: LinearGradient(
      colors: [Color(0xFF0057E5), Color(0xFF003BB5)],
      begin: Alignment.topLeft,
      end: Alignment.bottomRight,
    ),
  ),
)

// Card with shadow
Container(
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: Colors.white,
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16),
    boxShadow: const [
      BoxShadow(color: Color(0x14000000), blurRadius: 8, offset: Offset(0, 4)),
    ],
  ),
)
```

## State Consumers

```dart
// PREFERRED — auto-switches on {{STATE_TYPE}}
{{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(
  contextParent: context,
  onRepositoryLoading: (_) =>
      const Center(child: CircularProgressIndicator()),
  onRepositorySuccess: (repo) => _buildList(repo as XxxProvider),
  onRepositoryError: (repo) => _buildError(repo as XxxProvider),
  onRepositoryNoData: (repo) => const _EmptyView(),
)

// ONLY when watching a specific field
{{SELECTOR_BASE}}<XxxProvider>(
  selector: (ctx, p) => p.title,
  contextParrent: context,
  onRepository: (ctx, repo) =>
      Text((repo as XxxProvider).title),
)

// Low-level
context.select<XxxProvider, int>((p) => p.items.length);
context.read<XxxProvider>().fetchItems();
```

