## When to Create a New Widget

Create a new widget only when **all 3 conditions are met**:

1. No existing widget in this list or `{{IMPORT_COMPONENTS}}` fulfills the need.
2. The widget is used in **2 or more places**.
3. The widget has a **clear API** (props documented, no leaked external state).

If used only once, keep it inline in the body widget.

## Body Widget = StatelessWidget (NO ConsumerBase)

> **Nguồn:** `vnpt-workflow-stitch2flutter.mdc` + `architecture.mdc`

Body widget là **StatelessWidget thuần** — KHÔNG bọc `ConsumerBase`/`SelectorBase`/`ChangeNotifierProvider`.
`ConsumerBase` trong `buildRoot()` của `{{SCREEN_BASE_CLASS}}` đã xử lý loading/error/noData cả page.

```dart
// ✅ ĐÚNG — StatelessWidget, dùng context.watch/read/select
class BodyXxxWidget extends StatelessWidget {
  const BodyXxxWidget({super.key});

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    final items = context.watch<XxxProvider>().items;
    return ListView.builder(
      itemCount: items.length,
      itemBuilder: (_, i) => ItemWidget(item: items[i]),
    );
  }
}

// ❌ SAI — bọc ConsumerBase/SelectorBase trong body
class BodyXxxWidget extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return SelectorBase<XxxProvider>(...);  // ❌ KHÔNG làm vậy
  }
}
```

**Khi nào dùng ConsumerBase/SelectorBase?**
- Chỉ khi cần **loading/error riêng** cho từng thành phần (ví dụ: nút Submit có loading riêng).

## Review Checklist for New Widget in PR

- [ ] Searched `{{IMPORT_COMPONENTS}}` first.
- [ ] Used in at least 2 places.
- [ ] Props are clearly named and documented.
- [ ] Uses `{{BRAND}}`, `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.*`, `{{I18N_GETTER}}`.
- [ ] If screen-level reusable component → consider placing in `{{IMPORT_COMPONENTS}}` for future reuse.
